    "metadata": {
        "sysdescription": "Eyukua is a warm, garden-heavy system settled predominantly by the Veldari\u2014stoic, long-lived agronomists who build communities around soil stewardship and conservative bio-engineering. Their exports are practical: resilient crops, clean organics, and medical packs designed for remote systems where a broken bone can become a death sentence. Eyukua dislikes \u201cheroics\u201d; they prefer prevention, redundancy, and quiet competence\u2014until someone threatens their seed vaults.",
